To be considered for a role with us, you'll bring the following:

o Passion about coding. Your idea of fun is probably to write an app in your spare time, be it a web 2.0 app or a shiny new framework to bring more fun to your daily activities

o Development and delivery experience with Java. Expect to show us a bit of your talent

o Analysis, design, coding and implementation of large-scale custom-built OO applications

o Keen to work collaboratively with intelligent people, sharing your ideas to solve real business problems

o Strong communication skills with the ability to work in a consulting environment and build relationships

And we will really value if you have:

o Strong knowledge of design patterns, refactoring and unit testing

o Experience working with Agile methods, including Extreme Programming (XP), Scrum and/or Kanban

o Experience with picking and applying good software practices like test driven development (TDD), continuous integration and continuous delivery

o Active participation in the professional community as a speaker, author or online contributor
